title: BIG FACTS feat. BENNY THE BUTCHER

description:
BIG BANK, DJ SCREAM and JADE have a roundtable discussion about lazy record executives, rapper starter kits and bad hygiene.

BENNY THE BUTCHER joins the BIG FACTS crew for an in depth discussion about his past street life, working with DRAKE, mentorship from JAY-Z, getting shot in November 2020 and more!
